title: Russell Wilson, Rams, Aaron Rodgers, and the Blazing 5
itunes:title: Russell Wilson, Rams, Aaron Rodgers, and the Blazing 5
description:
Colin discusses the Rams-Seahawks game, the great play of QB Russell Wilson, the problems with the Rams, what Packers QB Aaron Rodgers needs to do, and his Blazing 5 picks for the weekend. Guests include Hulk Hogan, Brock Huard, Drew Bledsoe, and Jason McIntyre.
